{"title":"别","date":"2019-11-17T04:52:20.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2019年11月17日","L":"2019/11/17","MM-DD":"11-17"},"thumbnail":"https://i.loli.net/2019/12/30/Y48Rj3kIgnomOBU.jpg","link":"2019/11/17/别","comments":true,"tags":["诗"],"updated":"2020-02-10T16:54:15.875Z","content":"<blockquote><p>黎明到黄昏，终点就是起点。</p>\n<footer><strong>——佐伊</strong></footer></blockquote><a id=\"more\"></a><p>我从日暮醒来<br>黑夜，无尽，寂静<br>混沌的思绪<br>涣散的情恸  </p>\n<p>长夜将尽<br>随手拾回几个残片<br>松软而咸涩  </p>\n<p>我伴初阳睡去<br>金霞，须臾，寂静<br>无言的话语<br>虚无的抚慰  </p>\n<p>晨曦愈烈<br>回首告别每个故人<br>微凉而清冽  </p>\n","prev":{"title":"献给每一个清晨","link":"2019/11/19/献给每一个清晨"},"next":{"title":"光","link":"2019/11/10/光"},"plink":"http://wardzhou.art/2019/11/17/别/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"白桦树下的人","link":"<a href=\"http://wardzhou.art/2019/11/17/别/\" title=\"别\">http://wardzhou.art/2019/11/17/别/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}